<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q20_v4" title="Q20_v4" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Se utiliza la siguiente expresión para representar la cantidad de cajas en un depósito:
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>7</m:mn>
          <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>10</m:mn>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>10</m:mn>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>8</m:mn>
          <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>10</m:mn>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>.
      
      ¿Cuál de las siguientes afirmaciones describe correctamente esa cantidad de cajas?
    </p>
    <p>Selecciona la descripción de valor posicional que interpreta correctamente esa descomposición.</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuál de las siguientes descripciones interpreta correctamente el modelo algebraico presentado?</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">Hay setenta mil trescientos ocho cajas.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión representa <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>70&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>70&#160;380</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Esta opción dice 70 308, pero <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>70&#160;308</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>70&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, que no coincide con 80 en las decenas.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">Hay setenta mil trescientos ochenta cajas.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La expresión representa <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>70&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>70&#160;380</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Eso se lee como setenta mil trescientos ochenta cajas.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">Hay setecientos tres mil ochenta cajas.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión representa <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>70&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>70&#160;380</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Esta opción dice 703 080, pero <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>703&#160;080</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math>, y en la expresión dada no aparece <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> ni <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">Hay setenta mil treinta y ocho cajas.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión representa <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>70&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>70&#160;380</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Esta opción dice 70 038, pero <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>70&#160;038</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>70&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y eso no coincide con 300 y 80 de la descomposición dada.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Interpretar cada término de la expresión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Cada término representa un valor posicional:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>70&#160;000</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>100</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>300</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>80</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Sumar las cantidades</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>70&#160;000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>300</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>80</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>70&#160;380</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Leer el número obtenido</strong></p>
            <p>El número 70 380 se lee como <strong>setenta mil trescientos ochenta</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La única alternativa que coincide exactamente con 70 380 es la <strong>opción B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La afirmación correcta es: <strong>Hay setenta mil trescientos ochenta cajas.</strong></p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>